<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN367">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>nākat taṉṉa pākār maṇṭilan</l>
<l>tamavē yāyiṉun tam<supplied>moṭu cellā</supplied></l>
<l>vēṟṟō rāyiṉu nōṟṟōrk koḻiyu</l>
<l>mēṟṟa pārppārk kīrṅkai niṟaiyap</l>
<l>pūvum poṉṉum puṉalpaṭac corintu</l>
<l>pāciḻai makaḷir polaṅkalat tēntiya</l>
<l>nārari tēṟaṉ <supplied>mānti</supplied> makiḻ<supplied>ciṟan</supplied></l>
<l>tiravalark karuṅkala marukātu vīci</l>
<l>vāḻtal vēṇṭumivaṇ varainta vaikal</l>
<l>vāḻac ceyta nalviṉai yalla</l>
<l>tāḻuṅ kālaip puṇaipiṟi tillai</l>
<l>yoṉṟupurin taṭaṅkiya virupiṟap pāḷar</l>
<l>muttīp puraiyak kāṇtaka virunta</l>
<l>koṟṟa veṇkuṭaik koṭittēr vēntir</l>
<l>yāṉaṟi yaḷavaiyō vituvē vāṉattu</l>
<l>vayaṅkit tōṉṟu mīṉiṉu mimmeṉa</l>
<l>viyaṅku māmaḻai yuṟaiyiṉu</l>
<l>muyarntumēn tōṉṟip polikanun nāḷē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Although the orb full of fates, like [that of] the snakes,</l>
<l>was their’s, it did not go with them. (1f.)</l>
<l>Although they were different ones, it stayed behind for those who were toiling. (3)</l>
<l>It is necessary to live, in the days here that are limited, (9)</l>
<l>showering without stinting precious ornaments to mendicants, (8)</l>
<l>exulting in delight, drinking toddy filtered through fibres (7)</l>
<l>that is offered from golden vessels by women with green[golden] jewels, (6)</l>
<l>pouring so that flowers and gold fall in a flood (5)</l>
<l>to fill the moist hands of the receiving brahmins. (4)</l>
<l>Apart from the good deeds performed while living (10)</l>
<l>there is no other support at the time one sinks. (11) </l>
<l>You kings with bannered chariots [and] victorious white parasols (14)</l>
<l>who sit, fit to be seen, like the three fires (13)</l>
<l>of the men with two birth who desire [and] retain one thing, (12)</l>
<l>as far as I know it is this. (15a-c)</l>
<l>May your days of appearing on top be more numerous (18)</l>
<l>more than the drops from dark clouds that move (17)</l>
<l>noisily, more than the flashes of lightning that appear glowing in the sky. (15df.)</l>
</lg>
